<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Links Favoritos - Solução Interna DimDim</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        .hero {
            background: #764ba2;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-logo {
            width: 120px;
        }
        .hero::before, .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        .hero::before {
            width: 300px; height: 300px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            top: -50px; left: -100px;
        }
        .hero::after {
            width: 200px; height: 200px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            bottom: -50px; right: -50px;
        }
        .feature-box {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .feature-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {{> partials/header}}
    <section class="hero text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <img src="/images/dimdim-logo.png" alt="DimDim Logo" class="hero-logo mb-4">
            <h1 class="display-4 mb-3">Links Favoritos</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-4">Solução interna da DimDim para guardar seus links empresariais e pessoais de forma rápida e segura.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Começar Agora</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box h-100">
                        <div class="feature-icon">💼</div>
                        <h5>Gerencie Links Empresariais</h5>
                        <p>Organize URLs de projetos, relatórios e ferramentas corporativas em um só lugar.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box h-100">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🏠</div>
                        <h5>Armazene Links Pessoais</h5>
                        <p>Guarde suas referências, tutoriais e sites favoritos para acesso rápido.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box h-100">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
                        <h5>Acesso Seguro</h5>
                        <p>Dados criptografados e login protegido via Spring Security.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="bg-light text-center py-3">
        <div class="container">
            <small>© 2025 DimDim. Todos os direitos reservados.</small>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>